{"synckey":1645929722,"updated":[{"bookId":"3300010689","bookmarkId":"3300010689_1_2149-2367","chapterUid":1,"markText":"布朗请我坐下来，开始询问我的背景、学历、专业，我这才感到“有门儿”了。从现在看来，不能说布朗势利眼，他只是按华尔街的游戏规则办事。这也是华尔街给我上的第一课：当一个人还未开口说话，还没有机会展示才华时，别人就只能根据外表来判断他是否懂得行规。有一句英语叫“First impression last”（最初的印象永不改变）。试想，一个正常的上班族，一天24小时除去吃饭、睡觉和通勤，每天最长的时间是和同事相处，有谁喜欢与不顺眼的人共事？","range":"2149-2367","createTime":1645929722,"type":1}],"removed":[],"chapters":[{"title":"自序","chapterUid":1,"chapterIdx":2}],"book":{"bookId":"3300010689","version":390992231,"format":"epub","soldout":0,"bookStatus":1,"cover":"https://cdn.weread.qq.com/weread/cover/89/3300010689/s_3300010689.jpg","title":"投资的方法：来自华尔街的金融投资课","author":"[加]陈思进","coverBoxInfo":{"blurhash":"K4JNqTt.$wH=MwtR4UrqtR","colors":[{"key":"1/4","hex":"#370e15"},{"key":"1/6","hex":"#400213"},{"key":"1/8","hex":"#480012"},{"key":"2/4","hex":"#4d2524"},{"key":"2/6","hex":"#571d1f"},{"key":"2/8","hex":"#611119"},{"key":"3/4","hex":"#683b35"},{"key":"3/6","hex":"#74342d"},{"key":"3/8","hex":"#7f2b23"},{"key":"3/12","hex":"#93020f"},{"key":"4/6","hex":"#8f4e43"},{"key":"4/10","hex":"#a53e2e"},{"key":"4/4","hex":"#82544d"},{"key":"5/10","hex":"#c35944"},{"key":"5/4","hex":"#9c6f66"},{"key":"5/8","hex":"#b76150"},{"key":"6/4","hex":"#b6897f"},{"key":"6/6","hex":"#c48374"},{"key":"6/8","hex":"#d27c69"},{"key":"6/12","hex":"#eb6d50"},{"key":"7/8","hex":"#f09681"},{"key":"7/10","hex":"#fd8f75"},{"key":"7/12","hex":"#ff8768"},{"key":"8/4","hex":"#ecbdb2"},{"key":"8/6","hex":"#fdb7a5"},{"key":"8/12","hex":"#ffa07c"},{"key":"9/2","hex":"#f2dfda"},{"key":"9/12","hex":"#ffb997"},{"key":"1/100","hex":"#d27c69"},{"key":"2/100","hex":"#f09681"},{"key":"3/100","hex":"#ffffff"},{"key":"4/100","hex":"#F3E5E8"},{"key":"5/100","hex":"#F3E5E8"},{"key":"6/100","hex":"#270007"}],"dominate_color":{"hex":"#9d0910","hsv":[357.41126441913925,94.03281830442704,61.55500556041928]},"custom_cover":"https://weread-1258476243.file.myqcloud.com/bookalphacover/689/3300010689/s_3300010689.jpg","cust